org.apache.james.mailbox.model

Class SearchQuery.NumericRange

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.mailbox.model.SearchQuery.NumericRange
  • Enclosing class:
    SearchQuery

    public static final class SearchQuery.NumericRange
extends Object
    Numbers within a particular range. Range includes both high and low boundaries. May be a single value. Long.MAX_VALUE represents unlimited in either direction.
